cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.LG, cs.CR 

This paper deals with probabilistic deductive databases, which are a subfield of databases and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.DB and cs.AI are the most likely categories. The paper also involves logical reasoning and orderings, which are covered in cs.LO. The use of probability theory and the trilattice structure may also fall under cs.LG (machine learning) and cs.CR (cryptography and security).
